data.description: Now this is country living! Sitting on 8 private acres, this stunning updated ranch features a fenced front yard, wood deck and serene creek running through the back. Head inside and immediately fall in love with the spacious great room with a cathedral knotty pine ceiling, giving you that true "up north" feel! Updated kitchen adorned with a massive island, luxurious cabinetry and quartz countertops. Master suite complete with walk-in closet and full bath. Looking for a private space away from home, an office or in-law suite? Look no further! The detached 3 car garage has a fully finished and heated upper studio apartment with 1 bed and 1 bath! Not to mention the breathtaking view from the apartment balcony! This home truly has it all!
